{"tid":396293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"55歲女子美容院打針昏迷　兩女職員被捕　其中一名持雙程證","createTime":"2017-09-11T14:22:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T22:23:04.000Z","uid":35370,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7abb0086da7430b977f5209a4e81f70a9fcea0b7","tid":396293,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:22:15.000Z","msg":"明報： <br />\n<br />\n一名55歲女子下午到尖沙嘴柯士甸道耀基大樓樓上美容院「純美美容中心」做美容療程，疑職員為她注射含有腎上腺素的針藥時突然陷昏迷，職員報警將她送院。<br />\n<br />\n警方經調查後，晚上拘捕兩名美容院女職員，指她們涉嫌無牌管有第一部毒藥及違反醫生註冊條例。<br />\n<br />\n事發今午2時，美容院職員報案指一名女顧客接受注射後感到不適，其後陷入昏迷，救護車接報到場將女子送往伊利沙伯醫院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n補充：<br />\n<br />\n有線電視live講咗，其中一個持雙程證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"605ccd6f3bb19ac304c5bbef782f1010b485bf9e","tid":396293,"uid":35370,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:23:17.000Z","msg":"感謝黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ae37cf17c6e289c2c1187bbb6ae406aa2d71d9","tid":396293,"uid":35370,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:24:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">又係</span>"},{"pid":"e2d086051515fa61c5a189c7b2133d83685e0e21","tid":396293,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:25:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96f3fc47eed969d5c9a15457879b1b956e00ece","tid":396293,"uid":35370,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:34:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/no